=== GRAVITY_CHESS ===
# id: 62
# title: The Gravity Chess Puzzle
# chinese_title: 重力棋
# category: Puzzle
# mode: dungeon

A holographic game board hovers in the air, pieces floating at different heights. The game uses gravitational rules — pieces move differently based on their weight and the local gravity. A plaque says: "Checkmate to proceed." The AI opponent waits patiently.

* [Play and defeat the AI]
  ~ gain_radical("王")
  "王" (wáng) — king, ruler
* [Analyze the AI's patterns before playing]
  ~ gain_xp(25)
  "棋" (qí) — chess, board game
* [Hack the game to force a win] {requires: class == 3}
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "赢" (yíng) — to win
* [Reset the board to look for a simpler solution]
  ~ gain_xp(10)
  "新" (xīn) — new, fresh
